Workflow:
1. User -> Transportation Planner;
2. Transportation Planner -> Accommodation Planner 
   Transportation Planner -> Restaurant Planner 
   Transportation -> Attractions Planner (in parallel);
3. Accommodation Planner, Restaurant Planner, Attractions Planner -> Plan Checker;
4. Plan Checker -> Final Plan Summarizer;
5. Final Plan Summarizer -> End.

Description:
First, the Transportation Planner determines flights between New Orleans (MSY) and Louisville (SDF) for March 12-14, 2022, and daily locations. This framework guides the Accommodation Planner (single-person lodging in Louisville), Restaurant Planner (solo dining options), and Attractions Planner (Louisville-specific free activities). The Plan Checker validates budget adherence ($1,900 total) and logistical consistency. Finally, the Final Plan Summarizer compiles the verified itinerary into a structured day-by-day format.
